{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Google just dropped a major upgrade for Gemma 4.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f371761c24892a52ad150f28c4702343ae1b23ec7c995ecb24e3ae81259d5a88",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "It's called multi token prediction. And it makes inference dramatically faster.",
      "checksum": "sha256:948a6c0008ce97be30e1b888773b169da32e05714505e911981bb75f40c7cc9f",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 9
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Let me show you how it works. Here's the problem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3568784e12540a0495803844b23db4d4737404a957a694f213d6f65993f91f6a",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Gemma 4 generates text one token at a time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e2b8e17aca8c528c904fa22a8f3a2998a4ecc3495ee5b8be171296419d49d3a6",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 30
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Each token costs the same compute. It doesn't matter if the next word is easy or hard to predict.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a7733f4bb28b2493c2f6e77263dff81b8f7f6d2dfa20d1d0c1b9641ea7574bc5",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 6.0836281179138325,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "So when the model is finishing the phrase actions speak louder than words, it's wasting cycles on the obvious part.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1bcc15f2381b61ee7825cf666bfa404d31e6dc9ed61254e79914004b1576e2e9",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 5.944308390022676,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "A smaller model could finish that sentence just as well.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9ed477714dec01ecb89aa352153f48dc4b2a50380c08c7b43e8e0dfcf1d80e2b",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 78
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "The fix is called speculative decoding. A small draft model predicts several tokens ahead of the big target model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7ea946b931b72e98cc083caddc0d35ccec2ca6300f32d23b6bcd16bf4d6bfe9f",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 88
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Let's say four tokens. The target model then verifies all four in one parallel forward pass.",
      "checksum": "sha256:978f61675d73b9e67fbb937a5b8df9a130e81ce00978131ae74ad56d623fdbef",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 107
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "If the target agrees with every draft token, all four are accepted. If it disagrees with one, it accepts up to that point.",
      "checksum": "sha256:acc1edb50e96c24603144d3460b55d72be277f409cc640e4f44a5c8152efce8e",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 7.662585034013605,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 123
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Then it replaces the rejected token with one of its own.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6965c6a68adf88c7874998e7f812e094a81562afdbeb4a2dd2b59cc8b1655cc0",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 146
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Either way, multiple tokens come out for the price of a single forward pass.",
      "checksum": "sha256:71850932e67ebc5efdc04dfc897a400a4732527300a2c2276acc30b98f1a7302",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 157
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "That drafter is the multi token prediction head.",
      "checksum": "sha256:79f89ca72725f2f5cd3f1874a7e6bc86f23a7821caf7381a202372015787f516",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The blog calls it the M T P head. For Gemma 4 E2B, the drafter is tiny.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eb1a3f516de9c6da8d978068de1ef7fc5be8a917e9f5f4d4ba6b929b4fc8f399",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 179
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Around 76 million parameters. Four decoder layers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ae618269b35e4cd01500eb1fde0ace8e368ea48b17036d9e1c87657f0d9e555e",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 196
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "And an input embedding size of just 256.",
      "checksum": "sha256:274186292785beb3d9387630cbf63db3cd57824ac5c36d7256ce43379499e084",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 203
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "The dense model uses 1536. Three enhancements make this work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:922fdf566579d151299ecf49654b744093ee7ec3fff6532b16a2c03c9cb82862",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 211
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "One. Target activations. The drafter takes the final activations from the target model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6396a3c23b89a357afbad0bc831c0de57e7538e71fc7fa8475fc3824cfddc749",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 221
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "It concatenates them with its own token embeddings.",
      "checksum": "sha256:99dba4775856335267e9246ad2cf620245b8c7f8e9849ad283526905564b8473",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 234
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Then it projects the result down from 1536 to 256 values.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3bf9caeba5bee34696ede29f80b7be862b70493ac8aee9e10792b86e608819e4",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 242
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Why throw away activations the target already paid for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:92f435e18fce347c11e879a7fd4c43292a047c070236051bab73c4e3089d122a",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 253
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Two. K V cache sharing. The drafter does not build its own K V cache.",
      "checksum": "sha256:71ace2f1f7d708eb0ec26dcb97b05a11ba1b163c11c8891efa35487bf79dd9a9",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 262
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "It cross attends to the target model's cache.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1195e35660a477abaa88813965a8af8197b5f41a2ebf62864f72772b8c3a1652",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 277
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "For local attention, it reuses the target's last local cache.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ae8c3fe2f5b925aea0b5e628ab2c895afbf52402fcc5340dfe2641dc487310c8",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 285
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "The target's last layer is always global, so the global cache is shared too.",
      "checksum": "sha256:73e0e05244738476eac4894afff2804cb2838e6884219fb0a340ce5df9eb539c",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 295
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Three. Efficient embedder. The Gemma 4 vocabulary is 262,144 tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:394d1ef1f64cae24548dcfd811bb62d311ec92fef0145f03abb1a4515f453fa8",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 6.501587301587302,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 309
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Computing logits over all of them is expensive for a tiny model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:acc578ab995410c573c52067687c7630041f3e29cd6ddefdb814a23ad7320aa7",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 319
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "So the team clustered the embeddings by meaning.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c843ab7f6f678ac66f67d3dfe24ec7db625efec9aba61855a6ce910c9da5d829",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 331
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "The L M head computes cluster logits first.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3b7d248691e5d630488997a6e29ad97c260a8ce6bd21c6a135e02cc45354ec44",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 339
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Then only the tokens inside the top clusters get resolved. This trick applies to E2B and E4B drafters.",
      "checksum": "sha256:022f313271cfdda9ff0c5408ab4bf81d3598860680bc8dc9afa6400ec338f9de",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 6.455147392290249,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 347
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Put it together and you get significant decoding speedups, with similar output quality.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a7738d879f351649ba9505c74201733bc93fe640ed971b6e0d646514434619a2",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 365
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "That makes these checkpoints perfect for low latency use cases, and on device applications.",
      "checksum": "sha256:79a1352359b202073b197a1caf6faf9f19a5652966b5f9708377fdc392051843",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 378
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "The drafters are released alongside the main Gemma 4 lineup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:24243b0177a906f28b47818df73a38647c5d3edd17a49493543f4b24aa622a05",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 392
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "If you ship anything that runs Gemma in production, this is the upgrade you do not want to skip.",
      "checksum": "sha256:795894bb79a042e0dfaf090984b9fbaf6ed2d73cec5791c1a1b65986d4d514cf",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 5.804988662131519,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 402
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous A I community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:52899526ba4f39f730d5f328f00657542506b8da37fd99281ff15415b2f72bc9",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 421
    }
  ]
}